dmca.title: DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google
dmca.principal_name: Brand Protection Officer for Nike Australia

works.description:
The Nike Air Max 90s incorporate the Nike

swoosh logo which is being used without permission in relation to these  
shoes. We confirm a good faith belief that these items infringe upon the  

copyrights owned by Nike.

The site noted automatically redirects to http://www.newerictradings.com/ 

which is offering a range of counterfeit Nike items for sale.
